  <h3 id="top-rated-movies">1. Top Rated Movies</h3>

  <p>This endpoint is NOT authenticated (no API key is required!). This endpoint should:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>retrieve top-rated movies from <a href="https://developers.themoviedb.org/3/getting-started/introduction">The Movie DB API</a></li>
    <li>retrieve a maximum of 20 results.</li>
    <li>include the title and the vote average of every movie</li>
  </ul>

