<section class="dropdown">
  <h3 id="movie-details">3. Movie Details</h3>

  <p>This endpoint is NOT authenticated. This endpoint should:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Return details about a movie‚Äôs
      <ul>
        <li>Title</li>
        <li>Release year</li>
        <li>Vote average</li>
        <li>Runtime in hours &amp; minutes</li>
        <li>Genre(s) associated to movie</li>
        <li>Summary description</li>
        <li>List the first 10 cast members (characters &amp; actors)</li>
        <li>Count the total reviews</li>
        <li>List of first 5 reviews (author and review)</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Include the movie‚Äôs ID (in the Movie DB API system, not your application) in the path</li>
    <li>Note: Retrieving this information from the Movie DB API could take up to 3 different network requests (unless you find a shortcut!)</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Example JSON response:</p>

