<section class="dropdown">
  <h3 id="create-a-viewing-party">4. Create a Viewing Party</h3>

  <p>This endpoint should:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>create a Viewing Party record and create the necessary joins records to invite all the indicated users
      <ul>
        <li>Note: The DB should be able to keep track of which user is the host of the party</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>require a valid API key be sent with the request</li>
    <li>ignore any parameters in the request that are not allowed</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Example Request</p>
  <div class="language-json highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Juliet's Bday Movie Bash!"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"start_time"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"2025-02-01 10:00:00"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"end_time"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"2025-02-01 14:30:00"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"movie_id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">278</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"movie_title"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"The Shawshank Redemption"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"api_key"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"e1An2gAidDbWtJuhbHFKryjU"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">must</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">be</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">valid</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">API</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">key</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">for</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">host</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"invitees"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">11</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">must</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">be</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">valid</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">user</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">IDs</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">in</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">the</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">system</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>  </div>

  <p>Example JSON response after successfully creating a Viewing Party resource:</p>
  <div class="language-json highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"data"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
