<h2 id="extensions-and-explorations">Extensions and Explorations</h2>

<section class="dropdown">
  <h3 id="similar-movies">Similar Movies</h3>

  <p>This endpoint is NOT authenticated. This endpoint should:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>For a given movie ID, retrieve movie information about similar movies</li>
    <li>Retrieve similar movie data from The Movie Database API</li>
    <li>Include the title and vote average for every similar movie</li>
  </ul>

</section>

<section class="dropdown">
  <h3 id="viewing-party-info-where-to-watch">Viewing Party Info: Where to Watch</h3>

  <p>This endpoint should:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Require an API key in order to retrieve viewing party information</li>
    <li>When passed a given viewing party ID in the request path, return a list of video providers where the movie is available</li>
    <li>Return the video providers organized by rent vs. buy.</li>
  </ul>

